    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels brand new! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s super clean and drives like an absolute dream. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how gorgeous it is. Shoot me a message if you want to come check it out!",
